{
  "title": "Tender Spicy German Meat Stew",
  "description": "A spicy and dense German dish featuring fiordilatte and rest-meat, perfect for a lazy Sunday, this low-glycemic-friendly stew is cooked to perfection in a tandoor-clay-pot.",
  "cuisine": "German",
  "diet": [
